---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { hosts, show } from '../data/podcast';
import { u } from '../lib/url';
---

<Base title="About" description={show.description}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose-wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="title">What “Thinking With…” is all about</h1>
      <p class="lede">{show.ethos}</p>

      <div class="body">
        <h2>How we started doing this</h2>
        <p>
          Thinking With… began as a pedagogical experiment among three teachers of rhetorical
          theory. We wanted to record what it actually sounds like to read a difficult text
          together — not the polished summary you'd give in a lecture, but the live work of
          following an argument, getting stuck, doubling back, and occasionally surprising
          ourselves. The first season took the Preface to Hegel's <em>Phenomenology of Spirit</em>
          as a catalyst, and we've kept going since.
        </p>

        <h2>What the show is</h2>
        <p>
          Each season we take a single major work and stay with it. The point is less to explain
          these texts than to <em>think with</em> them — to treat reading as a practice rather than
          a transfer of information. Hegel, Deleuze, Heidegger, Derrida, Nietzsche: the figures
          change, but the invitation is the same. Think along with the text, with us, and with each
          other.
        </p>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>We are three academics who specialize in rhetorical theory.</p>
        <ul class="hosts">
          {hosts.map((h) => (
            <li class="host">
              <span class="host-name">{h.name}</span>
              <span class="host-role muted">{h.role}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="cta card">
        <p>New here? Start with any season — the point was never to begin at the beginning.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href={u('/podcasts')} class="btn btn--primary">Browse the seasons</a>
          <a href={u('/contact#subscribe')} class="btn btn--ghost">Join the email list</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .title { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.4rem); }
  .lede { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
  .body h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; margin-top: 2.4rem; }
  .body p { font-size: 1.12rem; }
  .body em { font-style: italic; }
  .hosts { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1.2rem 0 0; display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
  .host {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.3rem;
    background: var(--paper-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .host-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .host-role { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 0.15rem; }
  .cta { margin-top: 3rem; padding: 1.8rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .cta p { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
</style>
